  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Farmers market - enhancing access to profitable markets</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The farmers in the project area working with GLM Zambia have improved their productivity but the problem is that they are unable to access profitable markets. The objective of this project is to build farmers&apos; marketing capacity, strengthen existing market
 committees and market centres in the villages, create arenas for farmers to make business linkages, and to enhance transportation through donkey draught power.</narrative>
  </description>
